{"type":null,"faqId":10649,"title":"P6-U06   设置飞行模式","answer":"<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">注意</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：在飞行模式下，无线网络不可用。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.75pt;margin-left:63.8pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">方法一：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">更多</span><span>…</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，勾选<b>飞行模式</b>，打开飞行模式；取消勾选即可关闭飞行模式。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.75pt;margin-left:63.8pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31810\" /><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.75pt;margin-left:63.8pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> \n\t<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">方法二：长按电源键</span><span>-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">选择<b>飞行模式。</b></span><b><span></span></b> \n\t</p>\n\t<p style=\"text-indent:-12.75pt;margin-left:63.8pt;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;text-indent:-12.75pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31811\" /></span> \n\t</p>\n</span> \n\t<p>\n\t\t<br />\n\t</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1375","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397639083000,"seriesProductName":"EDGE-U00","visitedTimes":20,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":6,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":nu